      • isSpecific

        boolean isSpecific()
        Returns whether this entry checks against the item type and extra data associated with the stack. If this returns true, any ItemStack whose ItemType and manipulators match those of the template will match this entry; however, not all manipulators present in the template are required to match those in the item stack to cause them to match. If this returns false, any item stack whose ItemType matches that of the entry will match this entry.
        Returns:
        true if the entry checks extra data on the stack

      • getTemplate

        ItemStackSnapshot getTemplate()
        Returns an item stack snapshot for plugins to inspect this entry. The returned snapshot will match this entry. The size of the snapshot will always be 1.
        Returns:
        A snapshot that matches this entry
